latestIgtvVideos.title: MAGICAL SKIN-CARE INGREDIENT ? Is it really worth the hype?
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Review of the @lorealparis 1.5% HA Serum ✨

I was as intrigued as you guys are about the newly launched @lorealparis 1.5% Hyaluronic Acid Serum and I have been using it for a few weeks now and let me tell you it doesn’t disappoint. Hyaluronic Acid is a magic ingredient that one needs to add in their skincare routine! I’ve been recommended to add it in my skin care regime and this serum has the right concentration of 1.5%!

The texture is lightweight, nonsticky and absorbs quickly into the skin. The best part it has no alcohol, parabens and fragrance!

LOVE how hydrated and radiant my skin looks. Truly looks better and better with every passing day.

Comes in 2 sizes - ₹499/- for 15ML and ₹999/- for 30ML!

Direct link to buy - https://amzn.to/2P9yMKD

#magicofhaserum
